steps.html_instructions: Turn right to stay on Maruf Köyü Yolu
Merge onto Ankara Çevre Yolu/O-20 via the ramp to İstanbul/Eskişehir/E88

Exit onto Eskişehir Yolu/D200/E90 toward Polatlı/Eskişehir/İzmir
Continue to follow D200/E90

Turn left onto Mevlana Cd./D695
Continue to follow D695

Turn right onto Isparta Akşehir Yolu/Sanayi Blv./D695
Continue to follow Isparta Akşehir Yolu/D695

Turn right onto Isparta Konya Yolu/D330/D350
Continue to follow D330/D350

Turn left onto Isparta Eğirdir Yolu/D330/D350
Continue to follow D330/D350
At the roundabout, take the 3rd exit onto Doğan Kımıllı Cd.
